{"word":"κοινωνός","slug":"κοινωνός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰοινωνός, οῦ, ὁ</el>/<el>ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κοινός\">κοινός</a></el>] only <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ masc.\">masc.</a> in the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> ‘one in close association with’, <b>partner <a href='B:490 5:10'>Lk 5:10</a>; <a href='B:530 10:20'>1 Cor 10:20</a>; <a href='B:540 8:23'>2 Cor 8:23</a>; <a href='B:640 1:1'>Phlm 17</a>; participant, sharer <a href='B:530 10:18'>1 Cor 10:18</a>; <a href='B:540 1:7'>2 Cor 1:7</a>; <a href='B:650 10:33'>Hb 10:33</a>; <a href='B:670 5:1'>1 Pt 5:1</a>; <a href='B:680 1:4'>2 Pt 1:4</a>.</b> <el>ϰ. <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐν\">ἐν</a> τῷ αἵματι τῶν προφητῶν</el> ac-complices in the murder of the prophets <b><a href='B:470 23:30'>Mt 23:30</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κοινωνικός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κοινῶς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}